text: Tricca is a city of ancient Thessaly, Greece. Tricca may also refer to: *Angiolo Tricca (1817-1884), Italian caricaturist and painter *Fosco Tricca (1856-1918), Italian painter *Michele Tricca (born 1993), Italian sprinter *Tricca, a synonym for a genus of wolf spiders.
title: Tricca (disambiguation)
